<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12117</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19693</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>睡鼠坐到了爱丽丝的旁边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19693</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25209</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爱丽丝开始变大，她觉得自己应该赶快离开，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25209</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28412</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但她又对审判过程很好奇。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28412</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33639</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>于是她决定，只要还有空间，就不走。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33639</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38941</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你可以不挤我吗？” 睡鼠抱怨说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38941</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42988</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我快不能呼吸了。” 鹰头狮说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42988</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49266</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我控制不了。” 爱丽丝说，“我在变大。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49266</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54352</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你没有权利在这里变大！” 睡鼠说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54352</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>睡鼠的话让爱丽丝很生气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64452</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“胡说！你知道你自己也在变大。” 她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70030</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的，但是他没有一下子变大。” 鹰头狮说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70030</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78891</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他和睡鼠站起来，走到法庭的另一边坐下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78891</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84339</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>与此同时，王后一直盯着疯帽子看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84339</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87680</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她挥挥手，叫了一名士兵。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87680</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92874</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“把上次演唱会的歌手名单给我拿过来。” 她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92874</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97562</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>疯帽子听到这句话，又开始发抖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97562</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103038</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“马上告诉我们你的故事。” 国王生气地说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103038</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107140</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“要不然我判你死刑。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107140</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114928</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“陛下，请原谅我这个可怜的人吧！” 疯帽子用颤抖的声音说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114928</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120246</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我只是坐下来喝茶，然后茶会闪光……”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120246</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124081</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么会闪光？” 国王问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124081</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131212</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“茶，我们开始喝茶，然后……” 疯帽子回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131212</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137650</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我知道你们在喝茶。我又不是傻瓜！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137650</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146041</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王开始有点不耐烦了，“继续讲下去。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146041</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151849</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“茶闪光了以后，三月兔说……”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151849</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155909</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我没说！” 三月兔打断他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155909</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159690</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你说了！” 疯帽子坚持说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159690</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163253</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我否认！” 三月兔说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163253</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167573</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他否认。” 国王对疯帽子说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167573</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174229</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“跳过三月兔的部分继续说。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174229</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177635</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爱丽丝看了看陪审团。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177635</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188604</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>陪审员们在写字板上划掉了 “我否认！” 那句话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188604</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196155</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那两只豚鼠把写字板写得乱七八糟的。” 她想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196155</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201671</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“然后睡鼠说……” 疯帽子紧张地看着睡鼠，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201671</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208850</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>以为他也会否认所有事情，但是睡鼠已经睡着了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208850</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215690</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“然后，我又吃了点面包和黄油。” 疯帽子说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215690</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220002</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“睡鼠说了什么？” 一只豚鼠问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220002</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224815</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我真的记不起来了。” 疯帽子说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224815</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232271</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你得记起来，要不然我叛你死刑。” 国王说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232270</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238263</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>疯帽子手里的茶杯、面包和黄油都掉到了地上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238263</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245240</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他单腿跪下，“陛下，请原谅我这个可怜的人吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245240</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247771</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他又重复了一句。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247771</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252812</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你真的不太会说话。” 国王说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252812</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>257101</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇哦！” 一只豚鼠欢呼了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>257101</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261734</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一名士兵马上过来，把他带走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261734</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>268883</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果你只知道这些，那就退下吧！” 国王对疯帽子说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>268883</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>273961</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>另外一只豚鼠也欢呼了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>273961</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>276836</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他也被带走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>276836</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>281774</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我还是先把茶喝完吧！” 疯帽子说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>281774</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>284750</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他很快地看了一眼王后。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>284750</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>288329</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>王后正在看歌手的名单。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>288329</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>292072</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你可以走了。” 国王说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>292072</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>296119</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>疯帽子从法庭里冲了出去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>296119</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>302150</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“在外面砍掉他的头。” 王后对一名士兵说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>302150</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>308691</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，当士兵赶到门外时，疯帽子已经消失了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>308691</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>312051</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爱丽丝不敢相信地摇摇头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>312051</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>315309</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“疯帽子一点用都没有。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>315309</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>323813</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>按这种速度，我们永远都无法知道红心武士是不是有罪的。” 她想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>323813</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>330875</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“传下一个证人！” 国王说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>